{
  "stem": "7739.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And his Kommando was building roads, so I was attending to his personal needs, as his pupil.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I made sure his boots are polished, that his clothing is clean, and I was ready for any errands.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Whatever he said, I was ready to-- to obey.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this afforded me extra food sometimes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I could get extra clothing-- not extra, but different clothing-- like, say, instead wearing tattered pants, he would make sure I got a better pair of pants or a shirt or whatever.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we used to build roads.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So it was evolved already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Building roads involved surveyors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The surveyors were Germans, not prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They come out from outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They used to lay out the roads, and we used to build them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It also involved going to the railway, to the same railway siding where the prisoners used to come in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They used to bring in the materials for building roads or taking out the clothings and the gold and the jewelry to Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So you had access to the railway line, in a group, of course, under a Kapo, under an overseer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "One day, the people from Lodz came, in July, August.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I think it was August.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "People from Lodz used to come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They used to disembark from the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "As soon as they disembarked from the train, we were going out in a group to collect stones for building the roads.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This was a guise, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "My job was to jump on the wagon before they were cleaned up, rummage through, and see if I can find anything that the Kapo wanted-- wanted-- conserves, like canned goods.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I gave it to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever he did, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Conserves, salamis, which they brought from Lodz, and valuables-- money, gold.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
